description: The Honey Badger may not care but The Hungry Badger certainly does when it comes to serving delicious seasonal cuisine to the folks of San Antone.Local foodies are major fans of this truck’s fare, including their tasty tortas, crafted quesadillas, and “wow”-worthy wraps, made with tender Texas beef and other top quality ingredients. It’s clear that for the amount of care they’re putting into their food and service, the team at The Hungry Badger deserves a hefty badge of honor, so y’all should definitely come on by and give this decked out truck a try.
name: The Hungry Badger
